OL,3,CTeachers to earn while they learn with
OL,4,Cfee-free apprenticeship degree
OL,6,FTrainee teachers will be able to earn
OL,7,Fwhile they learn after ministers
OL,8,Fannounced a "game-changing"
OL,9,Fapprenticeship scheme providing cost-
OL,10,Ffree degrees.
OL,12,FThe Department for Education (DfE)
OL,13,Fsaid its teacher degree apprenticeship
OL,14,Fprogramme will offer an alternative
OL,15,Froute for people to become qualified
OL,16,Fteachers.
