OL,3,CTeachers to earn while they learn with
OL,4,Cfee-free apprenticeship degree
OL,6,FIt is aimed at those who are not able
OL,7,Fto take time out to study full-time
OL,8,Ffor a degree, including some of
OL,9,FEngland's 400,000 teaching assistants
OL,10,Fin state-funded schools, or staff
OL,11,Falready working in education
OL,12,Finstitutions.
OL,14,FApprentices will spend about 40% of
OL,15,Ftheir time studying for their degree
OL,16,Fwith an accredited teacher-training
OL,17,Fprovider while also gaining experience
OL,18,Fin the classroom to earn their
OL,19,Fqualified teacher status (QTS).
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/13
