OL,3,CTeachers to earn while they learn with
OL,4,Cfee-free apprenticeship degree
OL,6,FWith all tuition fees paid for, DfE
OL,7,Fofficials said trainees "won't be
OL,8,Fsaddled with student debt".
OL,10,FMaking the announcement in National
OL,11,FApprenticeship Week, Education
OL,12,FSecretary Gillian Keegan said: "The
OL,13,Fteacher degree apprenticeship will
OL,14,Fopen up the profession to more people,
OL,15,Ffrom those who want a career change to
OL,16,Fthose who are looking for an earn-and-
OL,17,Flearn route without student debt.
