OL,3,CTeachers to earn while they learn with
OL,4,Cfee-free apprenticeship degree
OL,6,F"It will be a game-changing
OL,7,Fopportunity for schools to nurture and
OL,8,Fretain talent from the ground up,
OL,9,Fhelping apprentices to gain the
OL,10,Fknowledge and skills they need to
OL,11,Fteach future generations.''
OL,13,FThe apprenticeship programme will take
OL,14,Ffour years and be available for both
OL,15,Fprimary or secondary prospective
OL,16,Fteachers.
OL,18,FIt will build on the postgraduate
OL,19,Fteaching apprenticeship by offering a
OL,20,Fwork-based route to attaining a degree
OL,21,Fand QTS, Ms Keegan's department said.
