OL,3,CTeachers to earn while they learn with
OL,4,Cfee-free apprenticeship degree
OL,6,FTo train to teach in secondary schools
OL,7,Fin England, applicants need to have
OL,8,FGCSEs at grade 4 ` equivalent to a C `
OL,9,For above in English and maths, with
OL,10,Fthose wanting to teach at primary
OL,11,Flevel also needing the same minimum
OL,12,Fgrade in science.
OL,14,FTeacher-hopefuls also are required to
OL,15,Fhave a bachelor's degree in any
OL,16,Fsubject, with some training providers
OL,17,Finsisting a grade level of 2:2 or
OL,18,Fabove.
