OL,3,CTeachers to earn while they learn with
OL,4,Cfee-free apprenticeship degree
OL,6,FTo support schools to offer the new
OL,7,Fapprenticeship, the UK Government said
OL,8,Fit will start a pilot scheme working
OL,9,Fwith a small number of schools and
OL,10,Fteacher-training providers to fund up
OL,11,Fto 150 apprentices to teach maths in
OL,12,Fsecondary schools.
OL,14,FTraining providers will bid to take
OL,15,Fpart in the pilot and trainees will be
OL,16,Frecruited from this autumn, starting
OL,17,Ftheir training the following year.
OL,19,FThe pilot will then be used to inform
OL,20,Fthe future of the programme, the DfE
OL,21,Fsaid.
