OL,6,FJennifer Coupland, chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe Institute for Apprenticeships and
OL,8,FTechnical Education, said: "Having
OL,9,Fthis alternative quality route into
OL,10,Fteaching should make a big difference
OL,11,Fwith encouraging people from wider
OL,12,Fbackgrounds into the profession,
OL,13,Fhelping with social mobility and
OL,14,Fmaking sure schools get all the
OL,15,Ftalented teachers they need.
OL,26,@pD@\OU
