OL,4,Cfee-free apprenticeship degree
OL,6,F"I think it is also really important
OL,7,Fthat this will provide extra support
OL,8,Ffor brilliant teaching assistants and
OL,9,Fother people working in schools, who
OL,10,Fwant to be teachers, to make that next
OL,11,Fstep."
OL,13,FBut the Association of School and
OL,14,FCollege Leaders said the new scheme
OL,15,Fwould not solve the teacher
OL,16,Frecruitment crisis.
