OL,4,Cfee-free apprenticeship degree
OL,6,FThe union said the "real answer" to
OL,7,Fdealing with the shortage involved
OL,8,Fimproving teaching salaries and
OL,9,Ftackling "high levels of workload and
OL,10,Fstress" that drive people out of the
OL,11,Fprofession.
OL,13,FGeneral secretary Geoff Barton said:
OL,14,F"We think this is a good idea in
OL,15,Fprinciple, but it is unlikely that
OL,16,Fteacher degree apprenticeships will
OL,17,Fprovide anywhere near the number of
OL,18,Fqualified teachers required to solve
OL,19,Fthe recruitment and retention crisis.
