OL,6,F"In any event, it will take a long
OL,7,Ftime before degree apprenticeships
OL,8,Fmake any impact at all on the
OL,9,Frecruitment and retention crisis being
OL,10,Fexperienced by schools and colleges
OL,11,Fright now, and we think it is likely
OL,12,Fthat the system will continue to rely
OL,13,Fon the traditional postgraduate
OL,14,Ftraining routes for the foreseeable
OL,15,Ffuture."
