OL,6,FLabour's Bridget Phillipson, the
OL,7,Fshadow education secretary, said:
OL,8,F"This measure is mere window dressing
OL,9,Ffrom a Conservative government that
OL,10,Fhas overseen a mass exodus of teachers
OL,11,Ffrom our classrooms.
OL,13,F"Teachers are leaving in their droves,
OL,14,Fwhile too few are being recruited `
OL,15,Fthe result of the Conservatives
OL,16,Fdestroying the crucial relationship
OL,17,Fbetween Government and schools.
